data.description: Welcome to your new home just south of Nisswa! Well situated between North Long and Round, you'll be right in the heart of lake country with this home abounding with garage space! Featuring a 24x46 attached garage with a heated workshop PLUS a 26x52 pole barn you're not likely to run out of space anything soon! Inside the home, you'll be greeted by a large entryway as you walk into your 3-bedroom home with hardwood floors, an updated kitchen, and a great deck leading out to a private backyard partially fenced on an oversized lot at 1.48 acres. Unorganized territory making it well suited for a home business location! More info coming soon!
